    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223470/extras/468e53be29a8cee79fbea08535defe54.avif?t=1765990895\" width=1560 height=163 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223470/extras/ce74a1e41b2db3fa1408c98597d3cefe.avif?t=1765990895\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223470/extras_big/ce74a1e41b2db3fa1408c98597d3cefe.avif?t=1765990895 width=800 height=83 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Conquero（征服者）</strong>是一款 3D 回合制策略游戏。旨在为玩家提供快速而有趣的游戏体验。除了节奏明快的玩法外，玩家还需要在合适的时间征服正确的领土，通过研究发展军队和建筑，雇佣雇佣兵，正确管理资源，并与合适的领主结盟，以成为整个地图的唯一统治者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223470/extras/1fb30b3212387d155dc84c456907892c.poster.avif?t=1765990895\" width=800 height=417 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223470/extras/1fb30b3212387d155dc84c456907892c.webm?t=1765990895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223470/extras/885be8977b9961901a5f7665f3288060.avif?t=1765990895\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223470/extras_big/885be8977b9961901a5f7665f3288060.avif?t=1765990895 width=800 height=83 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223470/extras/1c0e4e08943c3d2c6f2958922401daea.avif?t=1765990895\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223470/extras_big/1c0e4e08943c3d2c6f2958922401daea.avif?t=1765990895 width=800 height=83 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>研究 -</strong> 通过研究建造建筑或增强军队力量</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建设 -</strong> 建造相关建筑来生产资源</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>幸福度</strong> – 提高民众幸福感以吸引更多人并提升税收收入</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>税率</strong> – 设置税率以平衡黄金收入与公民满意度</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>食物配给</strong> – 调整食物分配影响民众幸福度</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级军队和建筑 -</strong> 提升等级增强战斗力与效率</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>转换军队 -</strong> 将陆军单位转换为海军单位，反之亦然</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>雇佣兵 -</strong> 雇佣雇佣兵为你而战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>资源管理 - </strong> 仔细维护资源水平</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>商人 -</strong> 购买和出售商品以支持你的王国</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>边界 - </strong> 在其他领主之前抢占更多土地</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>围攻 -</strong> 围攻城堡和城镇以征服它们</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>灾害 -</strong> 应对农作物与军队中的不治疾病、森林火灾和暴风雨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>外交 -</strong> 向其他领主发送侮辱或赞美信件，或赠送黄金</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索遗迹 -</strong> 发现被遗忘的资源或建矿用的铁矿床</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>强盗与海盗 -</strong> 在森林或海边，你可能会遇到索要金币的强盗或海盗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223470/extras/8488c13d10b276ec186974dec303339f.avif?t=1765990895\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223470/extras_big/8488c13d10b276ec186974dec303339f.avif?t=1765990895 width=800 height=83 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
